text: Andrés Seperizza (born 6 November 1975) is an Argentine rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
